        </mxCell>
        
        <mxCell id="summary_text" value="Internal Flow Sequence:&#xa;1. Load crash data from artifacts → 2. Analyze and parse stack traces&#xa;3. Deduplicate by crash signature → 4. Assess severity and exploitability&#xa;5. Identify root cause with static analysis correlation&#xa;6. Generate minimal reproduction steps → 7. Compile comprehensive triage report&#xa;&#xa;Key Decision Points:&#xa;• Stack trace analysis determines crash type and location&#xa;• Deduplication reduces noise and focuses on unique issues&#xa;• Severity assessment prioritizes remediation efforts&#xa;• Root cause analysis correlates dynamic and static findings&#xa;• Reproduction steps enable efficient debugging" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=10;whiteSpace=wrap;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="930" y="1430" width="780" height="80" as="geometry"/>
